---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | TakeHomePay.nz"
  description="Privacy policy for TakeHomePay.nz. Learn how we handle your data and protect your privacy when using our New Zealand salary calculator."
  canonical="/privacy/"
>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-light py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center text-white">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/90">How we handle your information.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg max-w-none">

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Overview</h2>
      <p>TakeHomePay.nz ("the Website") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you visit and use our New Zealand salary calculator.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">No Personal Data Collection</h2>
      <p>Our salary calculator operates entirely within your web browser. All calculations are performed client-side using JavaScript. We do not collect, store, transmit, or process any salary information, income figures, or personal financial data that you enter into the calculator. Your financial information never leaves your device.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">No Account Required</h2>
      <p>You do not need to create an account, provide an email address, or share any personal information to use our calculator. The tool is freely available to all visitors without any form of registration.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Cookies</h2>
      <p>This website may use essential cookies that are necessary for the basic functioning of the website. We do not use tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or third-party cookies for marketing purposes. If we use any analytics services, they will be privacy-respecting and will not collect personally identifiable information.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Analytics</h2>
      <p>We may use privacy-focused analytics tools to understand general website usage patterns, such as page views and visitor counts. These tools do not use cookies, do not collect personal data, and do not track individual users across websites. Any analytics data collected is aggregated and anonymised.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>This website may use third-party services for hosting and content delivery. These service providers may collect basic server logs (such as IP addresses and access timestamps) as part of their standard operations. We do not share any user data with third parties for commercial purposes.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
      <p>Since we do not collect or store personal financial data, there is no risk of your salary information being compromised through our systems. All calculator operations occur locally in your browser. We use HTTPS encryption to ensure that your connection to our website is secure.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>This website is not directed at children under the age of 16. We do not knowingly collect any information from children.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Under the New Zealand Privacy Act 2020, you have the right to access, correct, and request deletion of any personal information we may hold. Since we do not collect personal data through the calculator, there is typically no personal information for us to provide, correct, or delete. If you have any privacy concerns, please contact us.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. We encourage you to review this page periodically to stay informed about how we protect your privacy.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, you may contact us through the website.</p>

      <p class="text-text-muted mt-8"><em>Last updated: July 2025</em></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
